{"tid":1968976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒：約翰遜遲了三日入院 留醫ICU一度「瀕臨死亡」","createTime":"2020-04-12T06:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T06:38:05.000Z","uid":89543,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75a0fa23be801cc8243eed22ea3baabef876c26f","tid":1968976,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/CHbNPqBCazjv5iyp6DPU8MCb2hA=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/L65WJC2AKVFIQHXRKHQ74D2DSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FCHbNPqBCazjv5iyp6DPU8MCb2hA%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FL65WJC2AKVFIQHXRKHQ74D2DSU.jpg&h=8e052b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國《星期日郵報》引述首相約翰遜的朋友表示，確診武漢肺炎的約翰遜比預期遲了三天入院，而且一度「瀕臨死亡」，內閣成員和助理都擔心得為他祈禱。雖然目前他正在康復，但專家相信他需要休養一段時間，隨時需時一個月才能恢復身體功能。<br />\n報道指約翰遜住院期間，雖未能與懷孕的未婚妻西蒙斯（Carrie Symonds）見面，卻收到她的情書及腹中骨肉的超聲波掃瞄，成為「強心針」。55歲的約翰遜上月27日確診武漢肺炎，自我隔離10天後仍然持續發燒咳嗽，上周日被送入倫敦聖托馬醫院，不久病情惡化，翌晚被送入深切治療部（ICU），至上周四病情好轉，轉送普通病房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《星期日郵報》報道指出，約翰遜保住性命後，向朋友表示，「國民保健服務」（NHS）救了他一命，對醫護人員不勝感激。內政大臣彭黛玲（Priti Patel）周六表示，約翰遜康復需時，閣員亦希望他此刻專心養病。<br />\n<br />\n英國有統計顯示，要送入深切治療部的武漢肺炎患者，只有約半數能夠存活，熬過這關的人至少也要卧床休養數星期。專家認為約翰遜如能康復，也要經過同樣漫長的恢復期，對抗病毒會令他耗盡身體所有能量，失去大量肌肉和力量。東英吉利大學（University of East Anglia）傳染病專家亨特（Professor Hunter）早前說：「明顯你會需要時間恢復。我會估計多數病得那麼重的人，需要至少一個月或者兩個月，才能好好恢復身體功能。」"},{"pid":"c5fe938d129272f9459eb69877afb5c35f995d50","tid":1968976,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200412/HMQNXUKSAGZTBAFBHXTADY3DFU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0NwT-ZMTltOW1YikRUMARIkm1fVMowRrJJLZUsCiVQ6EagB8E69Jf4QDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200412%2FHMQNXUKSAGZTBAFBHXTADY3DFU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0NwT-ZMTltOW1YikRUMARIkm1fVMowRrJJLZUsCiVQ6EagB8E69Jf4QDk&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W3Hr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=1d66f8ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200412%2FHMQNXUKSAGZTBAFBHXTADY3DFU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0NwT-ZMTltOW1YikRUMARIkm1fVMowRrJJLZUsCiVQ6EagB8E69Jf4QDk&h=3c1821f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200412/HMQNXUKSAGZTBAFBHXTADY3DFU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0NwT-ZMTltOW1YikRUMARIkm1fVMowRrJJLZUsCiVQ6EagB8E69Jf4QDk</a>"},{"pid":"762c4f30a05ac47b53f7cb4274eba3d11583e6b3","tid":1968976,"uid":25952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"死過返生 希望之後會對支那決絕啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2319cb707be1c1fe6423edd50caeaf7f9df9bf3","tid":1968976,"uid":18995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//約翰遜:華為建5G無損英美關係- <a href=\"http://信報網站hkej.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99hkej.com&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W3Hr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=ce46bcff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">信報網站hkej.com</a> - 信報財經<br />\n英國決定容許華為參建當地的5G網絡，英國首相約翰遜 表示，英國在獲得最佳技術的同時，又不損害與美國和其他盟國的安全合作，這一點「至關重要」。 約翰遜在國會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2363928//\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Fl